query:
SELECT
                bdl.id as "link_id: _",
                b.id as "block_id: _",
                b.title,
                b.created_at as "created_at: _",
                b.updated_at as "updated_at: _"
            FROM block_directional_links bdl
            JOIN blocks b ON b.id = bdl.block_to_id
            WHERE bdl.block_from_id = $1
